al/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢啲post多數上唔到熱門"},{"pid":"ca61fa55e09fd81d737fa0d02ab88dc1e5899ef8","tid":2039563,"uid":10241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T08:19:20.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n睇晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11baccefb20f93efbb00a7b31cc9d79553142c9e","tid":2039563,"uid":148315,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T08:23:16.000Z","msg":"其實佢啲文相當部分嘅對象係台灣人<br />\n香港人望落係呀媽係女人嘅嘢要解釋畀台灣人聽<br />\n呢點鄭立算有貢獻<br />\n早過周庭向日本宣傳"},{"pid":"cdd384189ab9a923774466177782509a8759c0c8","tid":2039563,"uid":28743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T08:35:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ec96fc91da5e6491a43c25ce582b8341412f62","tid":2039563,"uid":358640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T08:36:37.000Z","msg":"香港人愈擔心愈絕望愈要同全世界講<br />\n英國想知香港人及海外港人的民意以作下一步<br />\n衛報要人!!!<br />\n<br />\n[特急] 英國衛報收集港人對香港示威的意見 要相又要片 請認真填寫<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2039783\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2039783</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家可唔可以幫手COPY AND PASTE 去你的WHATSAPP GP TG ??<br />\n一個人SHARE 唔到咁多<br />\n<br />\n麻煩曬各位手足"},{"pid":"79ec6569cd31d4a37a94a3c0770f004b51c5e3ef","tid":2039563,"uid":149534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T08:37:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f5fa10dc1aa3c223386947915a6afed23e1b169e","tid":2039563,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T08:42:20.000Z","msg":"高汁分析"},{"pid":"b46718de72342d7f4fb2672179229d6fd2ee3b4c","tid":2039563,"uid":130797,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T08:43:24.000Z","msg"